      "settings": {
        "eyebrow_text": "About Us",
        "heading_text": "Passion to Purpose: The Story of DoggyJi",
        "body_text": "<p><strong>Ram Narayan</strong>, an engineer with a deep love for dogs, turned his concern for their well-being into a mission. While feeding stray dogs, he realized that glucose and other biscuits weren’t ideal for them. Determined to make a difference, he set out to create a healthier alternative.</p><p>After months of research, vet consultations, and testing, <strong>Doggy Ji was launched in January 2023</strong>. The goal? To provide nutritious, affordable, and high-quality food for dogs of all breeds, sizes, and ages.</p><p><strong>Doggy Ji makes feeding your dogs wholesome and pocket-friendly. It’s not just pet food—it’s a gesture of love in every bite!</strong></p>",
