            "text": "<p><strong>At Doggy Ji, we bridge the gap between quality and affordability in pet nutrition.</strong>While many brands offer healthy options at premium prices, we believe every dog deserves nutritious food, regardless of their owner’s budget. Our commitment to this vision has made us India’s pioneering affordable pet nutrition brand. Each batch of our products undergoes rigorous testing to ensure it meets our high standards of nutrition and safety.<br/><br/></p>"
